  "detailed_description": "I really like Counter-Strike and its level editor, Hammer. Thanks to the Unity engine, I believe I've achieved a combination of both: the easiest way to build 3D game levels and play quickly.<br>In this game, you can create a garden in sandbox building mode and then place some robots to play with you. After switching to FPS mode, you can compete with the robots in the garden and buildings.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927300/extras/9930206800007597b3a1324618422809.poster.avif?t=1723946662\" width=800 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927300/extras/9930206800007597b3a1324618422809.webm?t=1723946662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927300/extras/9930206800007597b3a1324618422809.mp4?t=1723946662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br>1. Use the easiest way to build a game level scene.<br>2. Play FPS games in your own scene.<br><strong>Note: After editing the scene, keep a support point under the camera before testing, as your starting point is the current position of the camera.</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "I really like Counter-Strike and its level editor, Hammer. Thanks to the Unity engine, I believe I've achieved a combination of both: the easiest way to build 3D game levels and play quickly.<br>In this game, you can create a garden in sandbox building mode and then place some robots to play with you. After switching to FPS mode, you can compete with the robots in the garden and buildings.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927300/extras/9930206800007597b3a1324618422809.poster.avif?t=1723946662\" width=800 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927300/extras/9930206800007597b3a1324618422809.webm?t=1723946662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927300/extras/9930206800007597b3a1324618422809.mp4?t=1723946662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br>1. Use the easiest way to build a game level scene.<br>2. Play FPS games in your own scene.<br><strong>Note: After editing the scene, keep a support point under the camera before testing, as your starting point is the current position of the camera.</strong>",
